15 people have been killed in a crash near Bundu Inn in Pretoria. Courtesy of #DStv403 * Editor's note: This is a developing story and will be updated when more information becomes available. PRETORIA - Emergency services have confirmed that 15 people have been killed in a crash near Bundu Inn in Ga-Rankuwa, Pretoria. Charles Mabaso from the Tshwane EMD said 26 others were injured, with seven in critical condition. Emergency services are on the scene. The cause of the collision is under investigation.